Paper: hep-th/9804127

Date: 1998-04-20

Title: Reply to comment by Zaslavskii on extremal black hole action

Authors: A. Ghosh (CERN) and P. Mitra (Saha Inst)

Comments: 1 page, REVTeX, adapted from reply in PRL 80, 3413 (1998)

It is shown that Zaslavskii's misunderstanding of our published proof of theirrelevance of all extremal black hole configurations (whether with equalcharge and mass or not) rests on his refusal to see the essential differencebetween the correct inequality governing extremal and non-extremal actions andhis incorrect version.